        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[#突击减肥小心横纹肌溶解#[裂开]心血来潮想“速成”减肥的朋友们注意了？平时锻炼少却突然长时间进行剧烈运动可能导致横纹肌溶解！过度运动或者节食不运动等极端...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BB%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E6%A8%AA%E7%BA%B9%E8%82%8C%E6%BA%B6%E8%A7%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%AA%81%E5%87%BB%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E5%B0%8F%E5%BF%83%E6%A8%AA%E7%BA%B9%E8%82%8C%E6%BA%B6%E8%A7%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#突击减肥小心横纹肌溶解#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>心血来潮想“速成”减肥的朋友们注意了？<br><br>平时锻炼少却突然长时间进行剧烈运动可能导致横纹肌溶解！<br><br>过度运动或者节食不运动等极端快速减重方法都容易造成横纹肌溶解，肌肉里的肌红蛋白大量进入血液，在通过肾脏排泄时会堵塞肾小管导致急性肾衰竭，严重可致命。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%2318%E5%B2%81%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E5%8F%8C%E8%85%BF%E8%82%8C%E8%82%89%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%91%E6%BA%B6%E8%A7%A3%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%AA%E8%82%A2%23&amp;extparam=%2318%E5%B2%81%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%A9%E5%8F%8C%E8%85%BF%E8%82%8C%E8%82%89%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%91%E6%BA%B6%E8%A7%A3%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%B4%E6%88%AA%E8%82%A2%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#18岁女孩双腿肌肉突发溶解面临截肢#</span></a> （央视网）<br><br>减肥还是要循序渐进，健康最重要！那么你们平常都是怎么运动减肥的，来一波分享～<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[举手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/fd/2022_raisehand_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[举手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/fd/2022_raisehand_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[举手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/fd/2022_raisehand_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hdbysukdijj20b40b4wh2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
