        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[[思考]#二阳是以轻症为主吗#？👇🏻#小卫疫点通# - 转发 @人民日报:&ensp;【#二阳是以轻症为主吗#？】#专家提醒未阳过人群接种疫苗#针对目前感染新冠病毒增多...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BA%8C%E9%98%B3%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%BD%BB%E7%97%87%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BA%8C%E9%98%B3%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%BD%BB%E7%97%87%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#二阳是以轻症为主吗#</span></a>？👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%96%AB%E7%82%B9%E9%80%9A%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%96%AB%E7%82%B9%E9%80%9A%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫疫点通#</span></a><br><blockquote> - 转发 <a href="https://weibo.com/2803301701" target="_blank">@人民日报</a>: 【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BA%8C%E9%98%B3%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%BD%BB%E7%97%87%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BA%8C%E9%98%B3%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%BD%BB%E7%97%87%E4%B8%BA%E4%B8%BB%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#二阳是以轻症为主吗#</span></a>？】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E6%9C%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E6%8E%A5%E7%A7%8D%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%93%E5%AE%B6%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E6%9C%AA%E9%98%B3%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E6%8E%A5%E7%A7%8D%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#专家提醒未阳过人群接种疫苗#</span></a>针对目前感染新冠病毒增多的现象，广东省人民医院发热门诊主任黄晶表示，“从目前发热门诊的情况来看，总体以轻症为主，一般是发热和流感样症状。其中有部分阳性病例是首次感染“。建议脆弱人群在初次感染后3个月，以及未被感染过的人群接种疫苗。详戳↓↓ <a href="https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404894429097099757" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_article_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">临床和病毒专家提醒：脆弱人群以及未阳过人群，都要积极接种疫苗</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/0033ImPzly1hdby1sllrjj60rr0fmdhm02.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br></blockquote>]]></description>
